===Derived terms===
*{{ARchar|شَجَرٌ}} (šájar) = trees (in general) ''(plural in meaning, but grammatically singular)''
*{{ARchar|شَجَرَةٌ}} (šájara) = a tree
*{{ARchar|شَجَرْتَيْنِ}} (šajartēn) = two trees
*{{ARchar|شَجَرَاتٌ}} (šajarāt) = 3 to 10 trees, some trees, a few trees
*{{ARchar|أشْجَارٌ}} (’ašjār) = (kinds of) trees
*{{ARchar|شَجَرَة النَسَب}} (šájarat an-násab) = genealogical tree

